reviews.comment: I like the color of these and that they have a pocket but these are totally see-through on me. They are also made of a very thin material so not as much compression as I would like.
reviews.title: Not squat proof

reviews.comment: These are the best leggings! So comfortable and flattering. Plus they have pockets. I have worn them hiking for many hours, lounging at home, and for beach walks. The high waist keeps it flattering over my extra weight. No problems with the waist band rolling. No adjustments needed while hiking or walking around.
reviews.title: Best leggings

reviews.comment: I have the Zella brand so thought I would try the Z by Zella. They are great!  Fit great and not see through. TTS 5’1” 110lbs. Purchased in xs.
reviews.title: These Did Not Disappoint

reviews.comment: These are great! I live in Arizona and they are lightweight which I did not expect. The pockets are super deep for phones, keys, tissue. They’re my new daily attire since working from hone and walking/exercising in the early mornings. I just ordered my third pair. They wash well and I hang them to dry. They’ve kept heir shape well. I highly recommend them!
reviews.title: Awesome. Just ordered my third pair!

reviews.comment: Great fit. Shiny material, with a decent amount of hold for a slimming look. I am 5’7”, 140 lbs, 27” waist and the Small fits perfectly. Buy the same size you do in all Zella leggings. The pockets are super deep too, which means my iPhone, doesn’t fall out when I take my pants off!
reviews.title: Love them

reviews.comment: Bought these to work out and wanted something high waist with a pocket. They are shorter length so will also be great in the summer. Fit snug but not too tight. I am 5'4" 130 lbs and Medium fits good.
reviews.title: CAPRI LEGGINGS WITH A POCKET
